OL,5, Are tax hikes and rule changes in Wales
OL,6, already seeing more second home owners 
OL,7, sell their properties?                 
OL,9,FSome estate agents say there are signs 
OL,10,Fof that, but others say not enough is  
OL,11,Fbeing done to ensure local people can  
OL,12,Fafford homes.                          
OL,14,FAll councils in Wales will be able to  
OL,15,Fset council tax premiums of up to 300% 
OL,16,Fon second homes from April 2023.       
OL,18,FThe Welsh government said it was       
OL,19,Fcommitted to using "immediate and      
OL,20,Fradical" action to tackle injustices.  
